1. Install Required Dependencies

OpenCV requires several dependencies, so you need to install them first:

sudo apt install libhdf5-dev libhdf5-serial-dev libhdf5-103
sudo apt install libqtgui4 libqtwebkit4 libqt4-test python3-pyqt5
sudo apt install libatlas-base-dev

2. Install OpenCV

sudo apt install python3-opencv

3. Install GStreamer & plugins

sudo apt install gstreamer1.0-tools gstreamer1.0-plugins-base gstreamer1.0-plugins-good gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad gstreamer1.0-plugins-ugly